  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would go-- the next barrack to us was a women barrack, and we would go pick up clothes in the women's barrack.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But his excuse was to go to see some ladies at the women's barrack and for us to bring the clothes back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] He [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] never mistreated me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He [SIGHS] gave me food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yes, it's a difficult question to say, but I'm gonna talk about it anyway.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He definitely tried take advantages of me, sexual, but never forced himself into me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He made me masturbate him by hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He tried once I should do a fellatio on him, but I refused, and he never forced me into it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Otherwise, he-- he definitely never mistreated in any way, or hurt me or-- or-- in any way possible.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my life in Birkenau was, for food, [? deal. ?] I never lacked food, so I physically was building up a resistance of food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The tragedy was that in Birkenau, after two months-- they had, every few months, they had a-- [SIGHS] when they went through the barracks to see who is able and who was not able, and took my brother to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I lost my brother in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There I was watching the smoke going up from the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, again, [SIGHS] life went on and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] as I say, I-- when they went in there I did not have hardship in-- in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was able to get stockings to wear on my shoes, food was enough, and my work consisted of pushing a wagon or throwing clothes into the boiler.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
